> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">How do you rate </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">the way in which the various </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">EU policies</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> have been applied in </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Ireland</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">? How would you rate the effectiveness of the different policies?</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Emer Costello:</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">I</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> would say that </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">I</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">reland</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> is one of the </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">real </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">success stories</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> of EU funding</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">. </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">The European Social Fund is particularly important. Last year we </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">celebrated 40 years</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> since our entry into the European Union and the referendum</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">. </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">I think </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Ireland</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> and the </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">UK</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> entered at the same time. </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">At the time </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Ireland</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">entered the EU, </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">from our perspective</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> there have been </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">huge advances</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> because joining the </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">European Union</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">, </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">or the Common Market as it was called then</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">, </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">opened up a huge market. Quite frankly, before that </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Ireland</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">was </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">very dependent on </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">the </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">UK</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">’s</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> cheap food policy. We were seen as </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">a mechanism f